    • start

      public void start(javafx.stage.Stage stage) throws IOException
      The start() method is called when the JavaFX application is launched. It loads the FXML file, creates the scene, and displays the stage.
      指定者:
      start 在类中 javafx.application.Application
      参数:
      stage - the primary stage for the application.
      抛出:
      IOException - if an I/O error occurs while loading the FXML file.

    • main

      public static void main(String[] args)
      The main() method is the entry point of the StudyJourney application. It launches the JavaFX application.
      参数:
      args - command line arguments (not used in this application).
